<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ayoob Activation Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #cb1d20; 
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #cb1d20; 
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #555;
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: #ffbf2e;
            color: #cb1d20;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #ffcf54;
        }

        .activation-code {
            display: block;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #cb1d20; 
            background: #fff4f4; 
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #cb1d20;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #777;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #cb1d20; 
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Ayoob Ecommerce!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Dear <%= user.name %>,</h2>
            <p>Thank you for signing up! Weâ€™re excited to have you on board. To activate your account, please click the button below:</p>
            <a class="button" href="<%= activationLink %>">Activate Your Account</a>
            <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can use the activation code below:</p>
            <div class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></div>
            <p>Please note: This activation link will expire in <strong>5 minutes</strong> for security reasons.</p>
            <p>If you did not sign up for this service, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
            <p>For any questions or assistance, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@ayoob.com">support@ayoob.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Ayoob Ecommerce Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
